  "response": "Marrying your childhood crush can be an incredibly special and unique experience. For many people, it feels like a dream come true and can bring a sense of fulfillment and happiness. There is often a deep emotional connection and shared history that can strengthen the relationship. However, it's important to remember that every relationship has its challenges and requires effort, communication, and mutual respect to maintain. Ultimately, the feelings and experiences will vary from person to person, but it can be a wonderful and rewarding journey for those who find themselves in this situation.",
